data.description: Step inside this amazing canal and pool front home built in 2001 with two car garage in the subdivision of Rotonda West Pebble Beach. Home in great condition, interior is mostly original waiting for its new owner to add their finishing touches. Roof is less than 1 year old. Electrical and plumbing in great condition. Home located in a great appreciating area in close proximity to restaurants and other attractions. Will be sold vacant with clear title. Priced to sell.
